  • Packages that use protocol.serverinstructions 
    Package Description
    ai  
    network.client.client

    protocol.serverinstructions  
  • Classes in protocol.serverinstructions used by ai 
    Class and Description
    ProtocolBoughtDevelopmentCard
    9,7 Entwicklungskarte gekauft (bought development card) If player buys a development card, Server sends messade to Client (it does not distinguish between Knight cards and development cards) The "development card" has to be hidden for other players as Unknown.
    ProtocolBuild
    Bauvorgang (Build Process) Server sends to client the newly created building object.
    ProtocolCosts
    Kosten (Costs) Server sends to client the cost required (Decrease resources).
    ProtocolDiceRollResult
    Würfeln (Dice Roll Result) Server sends to client the dice roll result.
    ProtocolLargestArmy
    9.10Größte Rittermacht(biggest knight prowess) Server sends to client the Message about the Player who has the biggest knight prowess.
    ProtocolLongestRoad
    9.10Längste Handelsstraße(longest road Server sends to client the message about the Player who has the longest road.
    ProtocolResourceObtain
    Ertrag (Resource Gain) Server sends to client the resources obtained.
    ProtocolRobberMovement
    Räuber versetzt (Robber repositioned) After robber's location has been changed.
    ProtocolStatusUpdate
    Statusupdate eines Spielers (Player's status update) After status of player changes.
